                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8834" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0029</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1184 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多方利益主体下新阳村乡村旅游价值共创之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Road to Value co-creation of Rural Tourism Value in Xinyang Village under Multiple Stakeholders</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭舒，曹宁，杨浩，刘欢，臧倩，姜曼，王昱慧，洛桑次成，王垒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">辽宁大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长卓扎西商贸有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者；价值共创；乡村旅游；新阳村</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stakeholders; Value co-creation; Rural tourism; Xinyang Village</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了黑龙江省鸡西市新阳村在成为煤炭枯竭型村庄之后，新阳村借助企业、村民、游客以及其他利益主体下，通过价值共创发展乡村旅游，实现共同富裕的故事。新阳村在成为煤炭资源枯竭型村庄之后，引发了生态环境遭受破坏、村里无持续收入来源、村民社会矛盾突出等问题，这些痛点亟待解决。在返乡人才的努力下，新阳村得到了省城决策咨询团队与长卓扎西商贸有限公司的帮助，将多方利益主体绑定，实现价值共创。本案例立足于市场营销中的“价值共创”的概念，结合利益相关者理论，帮助学生学习利益相关者理论、价值共创的概念、价值共创主体的利益诉求、价值共创行为和价值共创结果等知识。在案例中设置了一个开放性的思考题，锻炼学生对全局意识和发散思维的掌握，培养学生的核心素养。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the story of Xinyang Village in Jixi City, Heilongjiang Province, after becoming a coal depleted village. With the help of the government, villagers, and tourists, the village director of Xinyang Village developed rural tourism through value co-creation, and ultimately led Xinyang Village to achieve poverty alleviation and prosperity. After becoming a coal resource depleted village, Xinyang Village has caused problems such as ecological environment damage, lack of sustainable income sources in the village, and prominent social conflicts among villagers. These pain points need to be urgently addressed. With the efforts of returning talents, Xinyang Village has received assistance from the provincial decision-making consulting team to bind the three stakeholders and achieve value co-creation. This case is based on the concept of value co-creation in marketing, combined with stakeholder theory, to help students learn about stakeholder theory, the concept of value co-creation, the interests of value co-creation, value co-creation behavior, and value co-creation results. In the case, an open-ended thinking question was set up to exercise students&#39; mastery of global awareness and divergent thinking, and to cultivate their core competencies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《旅游消费者行为》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者；价值共创；社会交换理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
